Equation 18 shows that the conformational distribution of the macromolecule in solution is governed by the effective energy W. From Equations A18 and A15 we obtain

͐ p(q) ln p(q) dq ϭ ͐ p(q)5Ϫ␤W(q) Ϫ ln Z
ϩ ln Zww ϩ ln V8␲26 dq ϭ Ϫln Z ϩ ln Zww
ϩ ln V8␲2 Ϫ ␤ ͐ p(q)W(q) dq. (A19)

